<section id="features" class="features" aria-labelledby="features-heading">
  <div class="features-inner">
    <div class="section-header">
      <h2 id="features-heading" class="text-h2 font-bold text-text mb-3">강력한 기능</h2>
      <p class="text-lg text-text-secondary">전문가 수준의 도구를 누구나 쉽게</p>
    </div>
    <div class="features-grid">
      <article class="feature-card group">
